  "description": [
    "Lloyd George Sees Neutrality Of Russia as Important Factor Key Statesman of Former World War Insists England Should Bolster French Army to Avoid Humiliating Peace By David Lloyd George LONDONIt is just over 20 years ago that France and Britain signed the armistice with Germany which brought to an end the bloodiest war in history They are now fighting essentially the same struggle again Germany is again the aggressor Once more it is a fight for international rightthe recognition of the equal right of nations weak as well as strong to lead their own inde pendent lives as long as they do not in terfere with the rights of their neighbors This conflict has gone on periodically since the dawn of history It will go on for many centuries to come unless and until mankind accepts that principle as one of the irrefragable command ments of humanity That will only come to pass when the transgressor finds that the marauders path is too hard and too costly to travel In recent years it has been much too easy and too profitable The western democracies have once more undertaken the task of repeating the terrible lesson of 1914 to the same"
  ],
